dc_description_s: This data represents public lands for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2019, and includes the layers 'Washburn_County_Lands_2019', 'Washburn_Federal_Lands_2019', and 'Washburn_State_Lands_2019'.[County Forest: The County Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent County Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.Federal Lands: The Federal Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent Federal Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For complete metadata visit: http://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
